QuestionText: Based on the refund policy, how long does a client have to receive 100% credit back to the credit card account?
Answer1: They are only eligible for 50% back to their credit card account if the event is 30 days prior to the original rental date.
Answer2: They are never eligible for any refund.
Answer3: 30 days prior to the date of the event
Answer4: 10 City business days before the scheduled date of the event.
